name: Peak Power!
description:
After completing a structured warm-up, the session is conducted as a 'Free Ride'. However, you will be prompted to perform 6 x 3-5sec max sprints throughout the session. 



The aim is to hit your Pmax values. Sprints are very short @ 3-5sec, generally needing only 6-10 pedal strokes. Use any gear necessary to produce high power. 



Aim to choose a course with a minimal elevation gain for this session.
